{"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"text":"let","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"delay","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"UInt8","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:s5UInt8V"},{"text":"?","kind":"text"}],"platforms":["macOS"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"content":[{"type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The purpose of this field is to synchronize transitions initiated","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"by sending the same message multiple times with a short delay.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"For example, a Node would want to send a Generic On Off Set","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Unacknowledged message to a Group Address. In order to increase","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"changes of successful delivery, such message can be repeated."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"The first message could be sent with longer "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/NordicMesh\/documentation\/NordicMesh\/TransitionMessage\/delay","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"and each following with a shorter one, so when different Nodes"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"receive different messages, the action they take seems more"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"synchronized."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This file has to be set together with "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/NordicMesh\/documentation\/NordicMesh\/TransitionMessage\/transitionTime"},{"type":"text","text":"."}]}],"kind":"content"}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/NordicMesh\/documentation\/NordicMesh\/GenericPowerLevelSetUnacknowledged\/delay","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"kind":"symbol","variants":[{"paths":["\/do